OL,3,CBusinessman known as the 'Recycling
OL,4,CMan' pleads guilty to fly-tipping
OL,6,FA businessman, known in his local area
OL,7,Fas the 'Recycling Man', has admitted
OL,8,Ffly-tipping waste which he was
OL,9,Fsupposed to dispose of properly.
OL,11,FAndrew Williams pleaded guilty to fly-
OL,12,Ftipping after appearing in court on
OL,13,FWednesday, 7 August.
OL,15,FMr Williams often promotes his
OL,16,Fbusiness, Recycling Man, on Facebook,
OL,17,Fassuring that all waste is disposed of
OL,18,Fcorrectly.
