OL,6,FIn court, he admitted that the
OL,7,Fcontents of the shed were larger than
OL,8,Fhe anticipated and took longer to load.
OL,10,FThe council found that he "completely
OL,11,Fmiscalculated" the nature of the job
OL,12,Fand was unable to take it to any
OL,13,Ffacility as it was too late in the day.
